# ── Example 1: Study still being processed (202 Accepted) ──────────────────

# Request
GET /v1/studies/1.2.840.10008.5.1.4.1.1.2.999/result HTTP/1.1
Host: api.radiology-triage.internal
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJSUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9...

# Response
HTTP/1.1 202 Accepted
Content-Type: application/json
Retry-After: 2

{
  "studyId": "1.2.840.10008.5.1.4.1.1.2.999",
  "status": "inferring",
  "receivedAt": "2026-06-07T14:25:00.000Z",
  "estimatedCompletionMs": 1800
}


